<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContentdb20e3607f684c1890d181b31e522ffe">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="BMI The Clementine Hospital" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=115900"/>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<p><strong>BMI The Clementine Churchill Hospital in Harrow, Middlesex</strong></p>
</div>
<p><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-clementine-churchill-hospital" target="_blank">BMI The Clementine Churchill Hospital</a> provides services to adults and children age 16 and above. The hospital has 121 beds, five theatres, an endoscopy suite, a level 3 Intensive Care unit and offers a self-pay service.</p>
<p>We also treat NHS funded patients, and patients who wish to pay for their own treatment. To see which treatments are available for NHS funded patients, please look at the NHS Patients page on our homepage.Â </p>
<p>Here is a list of some of the treatments available at <strong>BMI The Clementine Churchill Hospital</strong>:</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-clementine-churchill-hospital/orthopaedic-surgery" target="_blank" title="Private Orthopaedic Treatment in Middlesex">Private Orthopaedic Treatment in Middlesex</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Arthroscopy for wrist, elbow and shoulder</li>
<li>Trigger finger treatment</li>
<li>Arthroscopy for ankle, knee and <a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/treatments/orthopaedic-surgery/hip-arthroscopy" target="_blank">hip</a></li>
<li>ACL reconstruction surgery</li>
<li>Navio Robotic-assisted surgery</li>
<li><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-clementine-churchill-hospital/physiotherapy" target="_blank" title="Physiotherapy in Middlesex">Physiotherapy</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-clementine-churchill-hospital/the-spinal-unit" target="_blank" title="The Spinal Unit in Middlesex">The Spinal Unit</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-clementine-churchill-hospital/sports-injuries-clinic" target="_blank" title="Sports Injuries Clinic in Middlesex">Sports Injuries Clinic</a></li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/treatments/imaging-and-radiology" target="_blank" title="Diagnostics and Imaging treatments in Middlesex">Diagnostics &amp; Imaging Treatments in Middlesex</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>CT scanning</li>
<li>MRI scan</li>
<li><strong></strong>Ultrasound</li>
<li>X-ray</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/treatments/cancer-care" target="_blank" title="Cancer Care in Middlesex">Gynaecology Services in Middlesex</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Heavy periods, bleeding between periods or irregular periods</li>
<li>Endometriosis</li>
<li>Infertility / reproductive conditions</li>
<li>Abdominal or pelvic pain during or between periods</li>
</ul>
<div>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/treatments/cancer-care" target="_blank" title="Cancer Care in Middlesex">Endoscopy services in Middlesex</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Bronchoscopy</li>
<li>Capsule endoscopy</li>
<li>Colonoscopy</li>
<li>Flexible cystoscopy</li>
<li>Gastrscopy biopsies</li>
<li>Sigmoidoscopy</li>
</ul>
<div>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/treatments/cancer-care" target="_blank" title="Cancer Care in Middlesex">Opthalmology services in Middlesex</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Ophthalmology consultation      and diagnosis</li>
<li>Cataract surgery</li>
<li>Corneal transplant surgery</li>
<li>Excimer laser surgery</li>
<li>Glaucoma Surgery</li>
<li>IOL vip system</li>
<li>Retinal detachment surgery</li>
</ul>
<strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/treatments/cancer-care" target="_blank" title="Cancer Care in Middlesex">Colorectal Surgery in Middlesex</a></strong></div>
</div>
<ul>
<li>Diagnosis of symptoms</li>
<li>Haemorrhoidectomy</li>
<li>Laparoscopic colectomy</li>
<li>Various other surgeries</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/treatments/fertility" target="_blank" title="Fertility treatment in Middlesex">Private Fertility Treatment in Middlesex</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>IVF</li>
<li>Assisted hatching</li>
<li>Cycle monitoring</li>
<li>Embryo cryopreservation</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/hospitals/bmi-the-clementine-churchill-hospital/weight-loss-services" target="_blank" title="Private weight loss services in Middlesex">Private Weight Loss Services in Middlesex</a></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Banded gastric band</li>
<li>Banded sleeve gastrectomy</li>
<a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/treatments/weight-loss-surgery/duodenal-switch"> </a>
<li>Duodenal switch</li>
<li>Gastric balloon surgery</li>
<li>Gastric band surgery</li>
</ul>
<p>BMI Healthcare offer the best <a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/patient-information/quality-of-care" target="_blank" title="Quality of care">quality of care </a>and services. For more information about our hospitals and services please visit the <a href="https://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="BMI Healthcare">website</a>.</p></div>
