<h4 id="Article-51678">Making healthcare affordable - paying for yourself</h4>
<div id="imageContent80e7ecf48e4b43f6a21b1dd28f76d734">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Paying for yourself" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_ArticleListModule_ArticlesRepeater_ctl01_ctl00_ArticleImage_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=36748"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>Need that important hip operation but are facing a long wait for your procedure? With our unique credit card, the BMI Card, private hospital treatment is now more affordable.</p>
<p>Or</p>
<p>A fixed term loan provided by Chrysalis Finance, allows you to pay in monthly instalments which can be spread over a time period to suit you.</p>
<p>Spread the cost of your treatment and get back to doing what you love, with BMI Healthcare.Â  <a href="http://www.bmihealthcare.co.uk/paying-for-yourself" target="_blank">Click here to find out more.</a></p>
